'''Thomas Emson''' is a British horror writer.

Eight of his novels have been published,<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.amazon.co.uk/Thomas-Emson/e/B0034Q4G8Y/ref=sr_ntt_srch_lnk_1?qid=1528966997&sr=8-1|title=Amazon.co.uk: Thomas Emson: Books, Biography, Blogs, Audiobooks, Kindle|website=www.amazon.co.uk|access-date=2018-06-14}}</ref> and he has also written a collection of stories<ref>{{Cite book|url=https://www.amazon.co.uk/Trees-Other-Stories-Thomas-Emson/dp/1517534496/ref=sr_1_1?s=books&ie=UTF8&qid=1528967053&sr=1-1&keywords=the+trees+emson|title=The Trees and Other Stories|last=results|first=search|date=2015-11-18|publisher=CreateSpace Independent Publishing Platform|isbn=9781517534493|edition=1st|language=English}}</ref> and a How to guide for writing novels.<ref>{{Cite book|url=https://www.amazon.co.uk/How-Write-Novel-Months-published/dp/1499592132/ref=sr_1_1?s=books&ie=UTF8&qid=1528967101&sr=1-1&keywords=emson+how+to|title=How To Write A Novel In 6 Months: A published author’s guide to writing a 50,000-word book in 24 weeks|last=results|first=search|date=2014-06-24|publisher=CreateSpace Independent Publishing Platform|isbn=9781499592139|language=English}}</ref>

Emson<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://thomasemson.com/|title=THOMAS EMSON {{!}} HORROR WRITER. DOG OWNER. MONSTER MAKER. COFFEE DRINKER|website=thomasemson.com|language=en-GB|access-date=2018-06-14}}</ref> lives in the South-East of England.

He is represented by Mariam Keen at the Whispering Buffalo Literary Agency.<ref>{{Cite journal|last=|first=|date=|title=Whispering Buffalo Literary Agency|url=https://www.whisperingbuffalo.com/|journal=|volume=|pages=|doi=10.5040/9781682660058.01|via=}}</ref>

